/.lake/
.DS_Store
/.ignore/
/.gauss/

# Cargo build artifacts for the `third_party/` hax demo crates. These
# are regenerable from the Rust source + `cargo hax into lean`; only the
# source (`Cargo.toml`, `src/`) and the emitted Lean
# (`proofs/lean/extraction/*.lean`) are tracked. Mirrors hax's own
# `.gitignore` convention in `.lake/packages/Hax/.gitignore`.
third_party/**/target/
third_party/**/Cargo.lock

# LaTeX compilation files
*.aux
*.paux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*.synctex.gz
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.bbl
*.blg
